 <title>week 1 </title>
 <link>http://archive.p2pu.org/introduction-finance-economics-mar-2010/discussion/week-1</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;br /&gt;
	Post initial response to each by Tuesday 1200 GMT and at least 2 responses to other students postings by Thursday 1200 GMT. Dont forget to cite references.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Discussion questions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;	1) Why do&amp;nbsp;countries have currencies with different values to each other?&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;2) How does a nation gain and / or &amp;nbsp;lose when the value of their currency fluctuates?&lt;br /&gt;
	3) How can&amp;nbsp; government&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;actions (central banks) affect the value of their currency and why do they do so?&lt;/p&gt;
